	quest.1CE0095340328C08.quest_desc: ["Still not satisified? You need to beat even more Trainers? \\n\\nThe Battleground includes even more Optional Trainers to fight! Also ones Spawning where End Cities Spawn. \\n\\nThese being &5Battleground Alice&f, &5Battleground Benjamin&f, &5Battleground Big Mo&f, &5Battleground Mel&f, &5Battleground Mirskle&f, &5Battleground Tessy&f, and &5Battleground Vega&r. \\nBeat all of them and you'll win the Battleground!"]
