	quest.6E7DC2CDA7147743.title: "&5Champion Jax"
	quest.76CA3D98A4772886.quest_desc: ["The &4&oSeries&r may be over but if you want to stay the &5Champ&r you need to fight to keep it! \\\\n\\\\nSome of the people who've lost to you before are coming back for revenge, and the title of &5Champ&r! \\\\n\\\\nThese being: &5Title Defense Jax&f, &5Title Defense Marlon&f, &5Title Defense Milo&f, &5Title Defense Solenk&f, &5Title Defense Wayne&f, and &5Title Defense Zeph&r. \\\\n\\\\nThese are optional Fights so unfortunately they don't have a Signature Item. Instead they will randomly Spawn in certain Biomes. (Hint: all are Biomes where End Cities can Spawn). \\\\n\\\\nIf you beat them all you will get the Borrius Title!"]
	quest.76CA3D98A4772886.title: "Still the &5Champ&r!"
